Migrate the rest of the interesting targets from the Makefile into the
simpler garden format.

tests: adjust syntax to appease treesitter

Treesitter get confused by the nested { brace inside
of the "expected" string. Adjust the code to avoid the issue.

Related-to: https://github.com/nvim-treesitter/nvim-treesitter/issues/1573
